Text: I've never heard of this before, but it looks interesting.  I'll try it out while I wait for someone to upload the new Smallville.  My cable compang dropped the WB.

Um, dude?  Get a clue!  WB is no more!  WB & UPN combined to make "The CW" - a dumbass name made by combining the first letters of CBS (which owned UPN) and Warner.  CW will be on one of the channels the old WB or UPN were on (I'm pretty sure they carried over Smallville - along with my somewhat worn fave Gilmore Girls).
